{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_CFlameRotate}}
'''A_CFlameRotate'''

(no parameters)

Adjusts the angle by 6 degrees and changes the velocity accordingly to keep the actor moving in a circle.

This code pointer is restricted to {{Class|CircleFlame}} and actors inheriting from it.

